y teleports up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space it can see. Then one of the following effects occurs, based on the fey’s chosen mood:</p>\n<p class=\"Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body\"><strong>Fuming.</strong> The fey has advantage on the next attack roll it makes before the end of this turn.</p>\n<p class=\"Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body\"><strong>Mirthful.</strong> The fey can force one creature it can see within 10 feet of it to make a Wisdom saving throw against your spell save DC. Unless the save succeeds, the target is charmed by you and the fey for 1 minute or until the target takes any damage.</p>\n<p class=\"Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body\"><strong>Tricksy.</strong> The fey can fill a 5-foot cube within 5 feet of it with magical darkness, which lasts until the end of its next turn.</p>\n</div>"},"duration":{"units":"hour","value":1},"formula":"","level":3,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":300,"supply":0,"value":"a gilded flower worth at least 300 gp"},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":90},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"con","source":"Tasha’s Cauldron of Everything pg 112","target":{"type":"creature","units":null,"value":1,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.QPAonw7HT7HW11WK"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":721204,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":5855036,"sources":[{"pageNumber":112,"sourceId":67,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Summoning"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/creatures/mammals/elk-moose-marked-green.webp","name":"Summon Fey","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"