{"_id":"8T605hmjrj8Kinpb","data":{"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":true,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"powdered rhubarb leaf and an adder’s stomach","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":"","type":""},"critical":{"damage":"","threshold":null},"damage":{"parts":[["4d4","acid"],["2d4","acid"]],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>A shimmering green arrow streaks toward a target within range and bursts in a spray of acid. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes 4d4 acid damage immediately and 2d4 acid damage at the end of its next turn. On a miss, the arrow splashes the target with acid for half as much of the initial damage and no damage at the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage (both initial and later) increases by 1d4 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>A shimmering green arrow streaks toward a target within range and bursts in a spray of acid. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes 4d4 acid damage immediately and 2d4 acid damage at the end of its next turn. On a miss, the arrow splashes the target with acid for half as much of the initial damage and no damage at the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage (both initial and later) increases by 1d4 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"inst","value":null},"formula":"","level":2,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":"powdered rhubarb leaf and an adder’s stomach"},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":90},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling"