{"_id":"FRGJ9qszd30Qrob2","data":{"ability":"","actionType":"save","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":"","type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","cold"]],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You cause numbing frost to form on one creature that you can see within range. The target must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, the target takes 1d6 cold damage, and it has disadvantage on the next weapon attack roll it makes before the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p>The spell’s damage increases by 1d6 when you reach 5th level (2d6), 11th level (3d6), and 17th level (4d6).</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You cause numbing frost to form on one creature that you can see within range. The target must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, the target takes [[/r 1d6]] cold damage, and it has disadvantage on the next weapon attack roll it makes before the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p>The spell’s damage increases by 1d6 when you reach 5th level (2d6), 11th level (3d6), and 17th level (4d6).</p>"},"duration":{"units":"inst","value":null},"formula":"","level":0,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":60},"save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"1d6","mode":"cantrip"},"school":"evo","source":"Elemental Evil Player's Companion pg 156","target":{"type":"creature","units":"","value":1,"width":null},"uses":{"max":"","per":"","value":null}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickDamage":{"context":{"0":""},"value":{"0":true}},"quickDesc":{"value":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true},"quickOther":{"context":""