{"_id":"HuoSr7me2eBvSLZ7","data":{"ability":"","actionType":"save","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":"","type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8","fire"]],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">You create a bonfire on ground that you can see within range. Until the spell ends, the magic bonfire fills a 5-foot cube. Any creature in the bonfire’s space when you cast the spell must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or take 1d8 fire damage. A creature must also make the saving throw when it moves into the bonfire’s space for the first time on a turn or ends its turn there.</p>\n<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">The bonfire ignites flammable objects in its area that aren’t being worn or carried.</p>\n<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">The spell’s damage increases by 1d8 when you reach 5th level (2d8), 11th level (3d8), and 17th level (4d8).</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">You create a bonfire on ground that you can see within range. Until the spell ends, the magic bonfire fills a 5-foot cube. Any creature in the bonfire’s space when you cast the spell must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or take [[/r 1d8]] fire damage. A creature must also make the saving throw when it moves into the bonfire’s space for the first time on a turn or ends its turn there.</p>\n<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">The bonfire ignites flammable objects in its area that aren’t being worn or carried.</p>\n<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">The spell’s damage increases by 1d8 when you reach 5th level (2d8), 11th level (3d8), and 17th level (4d8).</p>"},"duration":{"units":"minute","value":1},"formula":"","level":0,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":fal