{"_id":"M1xT6SrYhoMg2h4v","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"save","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d10","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>Until the spell ends, wind whirls around you, and you gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Ranged weapon attacks made against you have disadvantage on the attack roll.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You gain a flying speed of 60 feet. If you are still flying when the spell ends, you fall, unless you can somehow prevent it.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You can use your action to create a 15-foot cube of swirling wind centered on a point you can see within 60 feet of you. Each creature in that area must make a Constitution saving throw. A creature takes 2d10 bludgeoning damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. If a Large or smaller creature fails the save, that creature is also pushed up to 10 feet away from the center of the cube.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>Until the spell ends, wind whirls around you, and you gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Ranged weapon attacks made against you have disadvantage on the attack roll.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You gain a flying speed of 60 feet. If you are still flying when the spell ends, you fall, unless you can somehow prevent it.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You can use your action to create a 15-foot cube of swirling wind centered on a point you can see within 60 feet of you. Each creature in that area must make a Constitution saving throw. A creature takes 2d10 bludgeoning damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. If a Large or smaller creature fails the save, that creature is also pushed up to 10 feet away from the center of the cube.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"},"duration":{"units":"minute","value":10},"formula":"","level":6,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"self","value":null},"save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"trs","source":"Elemental Evil Player's Companion pg 160","target":{"type":"cube","units":"ft","value":15,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.yCRe6v8mUFqKCRV1"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2389,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":138177,"sources":[{"pageNumber":160,"sourceId":4,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Damage","Control","Movement","Warding"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/air/wind-swirl-gray-blue.webp","name":"Investiture of Wind","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
