{"_id":"MQv6GNwPv92GE65r","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"other","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"minute"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":true,"ritual":true,"somatic":true,"value":"a lead-based ink worth at least 10 gp, which the spell consumes","vocal":false},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You write on parchment, paper, or some other suitable writing material and imbue it with a potent illusion that lasts for the duration.</p>\n<p>To you and any creatures you designate when you cast the spell, the writing appears normal, written in your hand, and conveys whatever meaning you intended when you wrote the text. To all others, the writing appears as if it were written in an unknown or magical script that is unintelligible. Alternatively, you can cause the writing to appear to be an entirely different message, written in a different hand and language, though the language must be one you know.</p>\n<p>Should the spell be dispelled, the original script and the illusion both disappear.</p>\n<p>A creature with truesight can read the hidden message.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You write on parchment, paper, or some other suitable writing material and imbue it with a potent illusion that lasts for the duration.</p>\n<p>To you and any creatures you designate when you cast the spell, the writing appears normal, written in your hand, and conveys whatever meaning you intended when you wrote the text. To all others, the writing appears as if it were written in an unknown or magical script that is unintelligible. Alternatively, you can cause the writing to appear to be an entirely different message, written in a different hand and language, though the language must be one you know.</p>\n<p>Should the spell be dispelled, the original script and the illusion both disappear.</p>\n<p>A creature with truesight can read the hidden message.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"day","value":10},"formula":"","level":1,"materials":{"consumed":true,"cost":10,"supply":0,"value":"a lead-based ink worth at least 10 gp, which the spell consumes"},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"touch","value":null},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"ill","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 252","target":{"type":null,"units":"touch","value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.kqjV0dAIf0SKIHqq"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2153,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":138345,"sources":[{"pageNumber":null,"sourceId":1,"sourceType":2},{"pageNumber":252,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Communication"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/air/fog-gas-smoke-purple.webp","name":"Illusory Script","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"MWtHpmhBxHyQwdXw","data":{"ability":"","actionType":"save","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":"","type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You seize the air and compel it to create one of the following effects at a point you can see within range:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>One Medium or smaller creature that you choose must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be pushed up to 5 feet away from you.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You create a small blast of air capable of moving one object that is neither held nor carried and that weighs no more than 5 pounds. The object is pushed up to 10 feet away from you. It isn’t pushed with enough force to cause damage.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You create a harmless sensory effect using air, such as causing leaves to rustle, wind to slam shutters shut, or your clothing to ripple in a breeze.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You seize the air and compel it to create one of the following effects at a point you can see within range:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>One Medium or smaller creature that you choose must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be pushed up to 5 feet away from you.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You create a small blast of air capable of moving one object that is neither held nor carried and that weighs no more than 5 pounds. The object is pushed up to 10 feet away from you. It isn’t pushed with enough force to cause damage.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You create a harmless sensory effect using air, such as causing leaves to rustle, wind to slam shutters shut, or your clothing to ripple in a breeze.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"},"duration":{"units":"inst","value":null},"formula":"","level":0,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":30},"save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"trs","source":"Elemental Evil Player's Companion pg 157","target":{"type":"","units":"","value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":"","per":"","value":null}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickDesc":{"value":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true},"quickOther":{"context":"","value":true},"quickProperties":{"value":true},"quickSave":{"value":true},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true,"value":false}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.k0Pt6GdrPMKii09m"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2383,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":138110,"sources":[{"pageNumber":157,"sourceId":4,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Control"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/air/wind-swirl-purple-blue.webp","name":"Gust","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"Mp5G9uet3APWMeZb","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"save","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"a small piece of quartz","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["10d6","cold"],["5d6","cold"]],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You create a wall of ice on a solid surface within range. You can form it into a hemispherical dome or a sphere with a radius of up to 10 feet, or you can shape a flat surface made up of ten 10-foot-square panels. Each panel must be contiguous with another panel. In any form, the wall is 1 foot thick and lasts for the duration.</p>\n<p>If the wall cuts through a creature's space when it appears, the creature within its area is pushed to one side of the wall and must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, the creature takes 10d6 cold damage, or half as much damage on a successful save.</p>\n<p>The wall is an object that can be damaged and thus breached. It has AC 12 and 30 hit points per 10-foot section, and it is vulnerable to fire damage. Reducing a 10-foot section of wall to 0 hit points destroys it and leaves behind a sheet of frigid air in the space the wall occupied. A creature moving through the sheet of frigid air for the first time on a turn must make a Constitution saving throw. That creature takes 5d6 cold damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage the wall deals when it appears increases by 2d6, and the damage from passing through the sheet of frigid air increases by 1d6, for each slot level above 6th.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You create a wall of ice on a solid surface within range. You can form it into a hemispherical dome or a sphere with a radius of up to 10 feet, or you can shape a flat surface made up of ten 10-foot-square panels. Each panel must be contiguous with another panel. In any form, the wall is 1 foot thick and lasts for the duration.</p>\n<p>If the wall cuts through a creature's space when it appears, the creature within its area is pushed to one side of the wall and must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, the creature takes 10d6 cold damage, or half as much damage on a successful save.</p>\n<p>The wall is an object that can be damaged and thus breached. It has AC 12 and 30 hit points per 10-foot section, and it is vulnerable to fire damage. Reducing a 10-foot section of wall to 0 hit points destroys it and leaves behind a sheet of frigid air in the space the wall occupied. A creature moving through the sheet of frigid air for the first time on a turn must make a Constitution saving throw. That creature takes 5d6 cold damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage the wall deals when it appears increases by 2d6, and the damage from passing through the sheet of frigid air increases by 1d6, for each slot level above 6th.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"minute","value":10},"formula":"","level":6,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":"a small piece of quartz"},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":120},"save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"2d6","mode":"level"},"school":"evo","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 285","target":{"type":"wall","units":"ft","value":100,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-s