{"_id":"QE57OJSPEbSbDr4e","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"other","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>Roll a d20 at the end of each of your turns for the duration of the spell. On a roll of 11 or higher, you vanish from your current plane of existence and appear in the Ethereal Plane (the spell fails and the casting is wasted if you were already on that plane). At the start of your next turn, and when the spell ends if you are on the Ethereal Plane, you return to an unoccupied space of your choice that you can see within 10 feet of the space you vanished from. If no unoccupied space is available within that range, you appear in the nearest unoccupied space (chosen at random if more than one space is equally near). You can dismiss this spell as an action.</p>\n<p>While on the Ethereal Plane, you can see and hear the plane you originated from, which is cast in shades of gray, and you can't see anything there more than 60 feet away. You can only affect and be affected by other creatures on the Ethereal Plane. Creatures that aren't there can't perceive you or interact with you, unless they have the ability to do so.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>Roll a d20 at the end of each of your turns for the duration of the spell. On a roll of 11 or higher, you vanish from your current plane of existence and appear in the Ethereal Plane (the spell fails and the casting is wasted if you were already on that plane). At the start of your next turn, and when the spell ends if you are on the Ethereal Plane, you return to an unoccupied space of your choice that you can see within 10 feet of the space you vanished from. If no unoccupied space is available within that range, you appear in the nearest unoccupied space (chosen at random if more than one space is equally near). You can dismiss this spell as an action.</p>\n<p>While on the Ethereal Plane, you can see and hear the plane you originated from, which is cast in shades of gray, and you can't see anything there more than 60 feet away. You can only affect and be affected by other creatures on the Ethereal Plane. Creatures that aren't there can't perceive you or interact with you, unless they have the ability to do so.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"minute","value":1},"formula":"","level":3,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"self","value":null},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"trs","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 219","target":{"type":"self","units":null,"value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.ZXKM4S7JDxCaOvRc"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2019,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":136154,"sources":[{"pageNumber":null,"sourceId":1,"sourceType":2},{"pageNumber":219,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Utility"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-hold-pink.webp","name":"Blink","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"QLPflCmpqfMzefd6","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"heal","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"hour"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":true,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"rare oils and unguents worth at least 1,000 gp, which the spell consumes","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You touch a dead humanoid or a piece of a dead humanoid. Provided that the creature has been dead no longer than 10 days, the spell forms a new adult body for it and then calls the soul to enter that body. If the target's soul isn't free or willing to do so, the spell fails.</p>\n<p>The magic fashions a new body for the creature to inhabit, which likely causes the creature's race to change. The GM rolls a d100 and consults the following table to determine what form the creature takes when restored to life, or the GM chooses a form.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>d100</th>\n<th>Race</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>01-04</td>\n<td>Dragonborn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>05-13</td>\n<td>Dwarf, hill</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14-21</td>\n<td>Dwarf, mountain</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>22-25</td>\n<td>Elf, dark</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>26-34</td>\n<td>Elf, high</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>35-42</td>\n<td>Elf, wood</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>43-46</td>\n<td>Gnome, forest</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>47-52</td>\n<td>Gnome, rock</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>53-56</td>\n<td>Half-elf</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>57-60</td>\n<td>Half-orc</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>61-68</td>\n<td>Halfling, lightfoot</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>69-76</td>\n<td>Halfling, stout</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>77-96</td>\n<td>Human</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>97-100</td>\n<td>Tiefling</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table><div id=\"table-link\">@Compendium[world.ddb-import-haven-tables.Reincarnate: Race]{Open RollTable Reincarnate: Race}</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The reincarnated creature recalls its former life and experiences. It retains the capabilities it had in its original form, except it exchanges its original race for the new one and changes its racial traits accordingly.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You touch a dead humanoid or a piece of a dead humanoid. Provided that the creature has been dead no longer than 10 days, the spell forms a new adult body for it and then calls the soul to enter that body. If the target's soul isn't free or willing to do so, the spell fails.</p>\n<p>The magic fashions a new body for the creature to inhabit, which likely causes the creature's race to change. The GM rolls a d100 and consults the following table to determine what form the creature takes when restored to life, or the GM chooses a form.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>d100</th>\n<th>Race</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>01-04</td>\n<td>Dragonborn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>05-13</td>\n<td>Dwarf, hill</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14-21</td>\n<td>Dwarf, mountain</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>22-25</td>\n<td>Elf, dark</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>26-34</td>\n<td>Elf, high</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>35-42</td>\n<td>Elf, wood</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>43-46</td>\n<td>Gnome, forest</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>47-52</td>\n<td>Gnome, rock</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>53-56</td>\n<td>Half-elf</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>57-60</td>\n<td>Half-orc</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>61-68</td>\n<td>Halfling, lightfoot</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>69-76</td>\n<td>Halfling, stout</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>77-96</td>\n<td>Human</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>97-100</td>\n<td>Tiefling</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table><div id=\"table-link\">@Compendium[world.ddb-import-haven-tables.Reincarnate: Race]{Open RollTable Reincarnate: Race}</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The reincarnated creature recalls its former life and experiences. It retains the capabilities it had in its original form, except it exchanges its original race for the new one and changes its racial traits accordingly.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"inst","value":""},"formula":"","level":5,"materials":{"consumed":true,"cost":1000,"supply":0,"value":"rare oils and unguents worth at least 1,000 gp, which the spell consumes"},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"touch","value":null},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"trs","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 271","target":{"type":null,"units":"touch","value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.uM87aSmwBmQMHhYf"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2228,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":138642,"sources":[{"pageNumber":null,"sourceId":1,"sourceType":2},{"pageNumber":271,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Healing"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-flame-blue.webp","name":"Reincarnate","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"QRCvUu3oovTr8Iol","data":{"ability":"","actionType":"other","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":"","type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You extend your hand and trace a sigil of warding in the air. Until the end of your next turn, you have resistance against bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage dealt by weapon attacks.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You extend your hand and trace a sigil of warding in the air. Until the end of your next turn, you have resistance against bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage dealt by weapon attacks.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"round","value":1},"formula":"","level":0,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"self","value":null},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"abj","source":"Player's Handbook pg 218","target":{"type":"self","units":"","value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":"","per":"","value":null}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickDesc":{"value":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true},"quickOther":{"context":"","value":true},"quickProperties":{"value":true},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true,"value":false}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.RbmKuZe07nDONkou"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2307,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":155895,"sources":[{"pageNumber":218,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Combat","Warding"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/equipment/shield/buckler-wooden-boss-glowing-blue.