{"_id":"YwohzGY92Qp5BEqA","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"util","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":true,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"a pair of platinum rings worth at least 50 gp each, which you and the target must wear for the duration","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>This spell wards a willing creature you touch and creates a mystic connection between you and the target until the spell ends. While the target is within 60 feet of you, it gains a +1 bonus to AC and saving throws, and it has resistance to all damage. Also, each time it takes damage, you take the same amount of damage.</p>\n<p>The spell ends if you drop to 0 hit points or if you and the target become separated by more than 60 feet. It also ends if the spell is cast again on either of the connected creatures. You can also dismiss the spell as an action.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>This spell wards a willing creature you touch and creates a mystic connection between you and the target until the spell ends. While the target is within 60 feet of you, it gains a +1 bonus to AC and saving throws, and it has resistance to all damage. Also, each time it takes damage, you take the same amount of damage.</p>\n<p>The spell ends if you drop to 0 hit points or if you and the target become separated by more than 60 feet. It also ends if the spell is cast again on either of the connected creatures. You can also dismiss the spell as an action.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"hour","value":1},"formula":"","level":2,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":50,"supply":0,"value":"a pair of platinum rings worth at least 50 gp each, which you and the target must wear for the duration"},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"touch","value":null},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"abj","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 287","target":{"type":null,"units":"touch","value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.RnLsFGBObUJlJt3v"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2296,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":138930,"sources":[{"pageNumber":null,"sourceId":1,"sourceType":2},{"pageNumber":287,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Buff","Warding"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-flaming-diamond-blue-yellow.webp","name":"Warding Bond","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"Z2pT7E04vxOWryRZ","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"other","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":true,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You gain the ability to comprehend and verbally communicate with beasts for the duration. The knowledge and awareness of many beasts is limited by their intelligence, but at minimum, beasts can give you information about nearby locations and monsters, including whatever they can perceive or have perceived within the past day. You might be able to persuade a beast to perform a small favor for you, at the GM's discretion.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You gain the ability to comprehend and verbally communicate with beasts for the duration. The knowledge and awareness of many beasts is limited by their intelligence, but at minimum, beasts can give you information about nearby locations and monsters, including whatever they can perceive or have perceived within the past day. You might be able to persuade a beast to perform a small favor for you, at the GM's discretion.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"minute","value":10},"formula":"","level":1,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"self","value":null},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"div","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 277","target":{"type":"self","units":null,"value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.E6hdr