{"_id":"coEunWcf0int4IzO","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"other","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":false,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You teleport yourself from your current location to any other spot within range. You arrive at exactly the spot desired. It can be a place you can see, one you can visualize, or one you can describe by stating distance and direction, such as \"200 feet straight downward\" or \"upward to the northwest at a 45- degree angle, 300 feet.\"</p>\n<p>You can bring along objects as long as their weight doesn't exceed what you can carry. You can also bring one willing creature of your size or smaller who is carrying gear up to its carrying capacity. The creature must be within 5 feet of you when you cast this spell.</p>\n<p>If you would arrive in a place already occupied by an object or a creature, you and any creature traveling with you each take 4d6 force damage, and the spell fails to teleport you.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You teleport yourself from your current location to any other spot within range. You arrive at exactly the spot desired. It can be a place you can see, one you can visualize, or one you can describe by stating distance and direction, such as \"200 feet straight downward\" or \"upward to the northwest at a 45- degree angle, 300 feet.\"</p>\n<p>You can bring along objects as long as their weight doesn't exceed what you can carry. You can also bring one willing creature of your size or smaller who is carrying gear up to its carrying capacity. The creature must be within 5 feet of you when you cast this spell.</p>\n<p>If you would arrive in a place already occupied by an object or a creature, you and any creature traveling with you each take 4d6 force damage, and the spell fails to teleport you.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"inst","value":""},"formula":"","level":4,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":500},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"con","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 233","target":{"type":null,"units":null,"value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.01h5Ou1lU0fSYFtY"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2068,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":136603,"sources":[{"pageNumber":null,"sourceId":1,"sourceType":2},{"pageNumber":233,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Teleportation"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/air/air-burst-spiral-large-pink.webp","name":"Dimension Door","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"d8hvS5hYbuTClGvG","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"rsak","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8",""],["1d6",""]],"value":"","versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You hurl an undulating, warbling mass of chaotic energy at one creature in range. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes 2d8 + 1d6 damage. Choose one of the d8s. The number rolled on that die determines the attack’s damage type, as shown below.</p>\n<div class=\"table-overflow-wrapper\">\n<table class=\"compendium-left-aligned-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>d8</th>\n<th>Damage Type</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>Acid</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>Cold</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>Fire</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>Force</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>Lightning</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>Poison</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>Psychic</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>Thunder</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table><div id=\"table-link\">@Compendium[world.ddb-import-haven-tables.Chaos Bolt: Damage Type]{Open RollTable Chaos Bolt: Damage Type}</div>\n</div>\n<p>If you roll the same number on both d8s, the chaotic energy leaps from the target to a different creature of your choice within 30 feet of it. Make a new attack roll against the new target, and make a new damage roll, which could cause the chaotic energy to leap again.</p>\n<p>A creature can be targeted only once by each casting of this spell.</p>\n<p><strong><em>At Higher Levels.</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, each target takes 1d6 extra damage of the type rolled for each slot level above 1st.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You hurl an undulating, warbling mass of chaotic energy at one creature in range. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes 2d8 + 1d6 damage. Choose one of the d8s. The number rolled on that die determines the attack’s damage type, as shown below.</p>\n<div class=\"table-overflow-wrapper\">\n<table class=\"compendium-left-aligned-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>d8</th>\n<th>Damage Type</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>Acid</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>Cold</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>Fire</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>Force</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>Lightning</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>Poison</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>Psychic</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>Thunder</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table><div id=\"table-link\">@Compendium[world.ddb-import-haven-tables.Chaos Bolt: Damage Type]{Open RollTable Chaos Bolt: Damage Type}</div>\n</div>\n<p>If you roll the same number on both d8s, the chaotic energy leaps from the target to a different creature of your choice within 30 feet of it. Make a new attack roll against the new target, and make a new damage roll, which could cause the chaotic energy to leap again.</p>\n<p>A creature can be targeted only once by each casting of this spell.</p>\n<p><strong><em>At Higher Levels.</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, each target takes 1d6 extra damage of the type rolled for each slot level above 1st.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"inst","value":""},"formula":"","level":1,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":120},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"1d6","mode":"level"},"school":"evo","source":"Xanathar's Guide to Everything pg 151","target":{"type":"creature","units":null,"value":1,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.D4AEQeVOtGINKjoK"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":14761,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":154574,"sources":[{"pageNumber":151,"sourceId":27,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Damage"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-beam-purple.webp","name":"Chaos Bolt","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"dZFosLgDG810yAPm","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"other","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>For the duration, you know if there is an aberration, celestial, elemental, fey, fiend, or undead within 30 feet of you, as well as where the creature is located. Similarly, you know if there is a place or object within 30 feet of you that has been magically consecrated or desecrated.</p>\n<p>The spell can penetrate most barriers, but it is blocked by 1 foot of stone, 1 inch of common metal, a thin sheet of lead, or 3 feet of wood or dirt.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>For the duration, you know if there is an aberration, celestial, elemental, fey, fiend, or undead within 30 feet of you, as well as where the creature is located. Similarly, you know if there is a place or object within 30 feet of you that has been magically consecrated or desecrated.</p>\n<p>The spell can penetrate most barriers, but it is blocked by 1 foot of stone, 1 inch of common metal, a thin sheet of lead, or 3 feet of wood or dirt.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"minute","value":10},"formula":"","level":1,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"self","value":null},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"div","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 231","target":{"type":"sphere","units":"ft","value":30,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compen