{"_id":"lLT2yqoCIxWE0MlR","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"util","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"a few hairs from a bull","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">You endow yourself with endurance and martial prowess fueled by magic. Until the spell ends, you can’t cast spells, and you gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">You gain 50 temporary hit points. If any of these remain when the spell ends, they are lost.</li>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">You have advantage on attack rolls that you make with simple and martial weapons.</li>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">When you hit a target with a weapon attack, that target takes an extra 2d12 force damage.</li>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">You have proficiency with all armor, shields, simple weapons, and martial weapons.</li>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">You have proficiency in Strength and Constitution saving throws.</li>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">You can attack twice, instead of once, when you take the Attack action on your turn. You ignore this benefit if you already have a feature, like Extra Attack, that gives you extra attacks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">Immediately after the spell ends, you must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or suffer one level of exhaustion.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">You endow yourself with endurance and martial prowess fueled by magic. Until the spell ends, you can’t cast spells, and you gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">You gain 50 temporary hit points. If any of these remain when the spell ends, they are lost.</li>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">You have advantage on attack rolls that you make with simple and martial weapons.</li>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">When you hit a target with a weapon attack, that target takes an extra 2d12 force damage.</li>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">You have proficiency with all armor, shields, simple weapons, and martial weapons.</li>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">You have proficiency in Strength and Constitution saving throws.</li>\n<li class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted\">You can attack twice, instead of once, when you take the Attack action on your turn. You ignore this benefit if you already have a feature, like Extra Attack, that gives you extra attacks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">Immediately after the spell ends, you must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or suffer one level of exhaustion.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"minute","value":10},"formula":"","level":6,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":"a few hairs from a bull"},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"self","value":null},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"trs","source":"Xanathar's Guide to Everything pg 168","target":{"type":"self","units":null,"value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.awJc9x4xCTzWv7VN"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":14612,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":138261,"sources":[{"pageNumber":168,"sourceId":27,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Buff","Combat"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/fire/dagger-rune-enchant-flame-