{"_id":"nQPL50y6NsHn5Wzp","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"save","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"niter, sulfur, and pine tar formed into a bead","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You create six tiny meteors in your space. They float in the air and orbit you for the spell’s duration. When you cast the spell — and as a bonus action on each of your turns thereafter — you can expend one or two of the meteors, sending them streaking toward a point or points you choose within 120 feet of you. Once a meteor reaches its destination or impacts against a solid surface, the meteor explodes. Each creature within 5 feet of the point where the meteor explodes must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 2d6 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p class=\"s19\"><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> <span class=\"p\">When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the number of meteors created increases by two for each slot level above 3rd.</span></p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You create six tiny meteors in your space. They float in the air and orbit you for the spell’s duration. When you cast the spell — and as a bonus action on each of your turns thereafter — you can expend one or two of the meteors, sending them streaking toward a point or points you choose within 120 feet of you. Once a meteor reaches its destination or impacts against a solid surface, the meteor explodes. Each creature within 5 feet of the point where the meteor explodes must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 2d6 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p class=\"s19\"><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> <span class=\"p\">When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the number of meteors created increases by two for each slot level above 3rd.</span></p>"},"duration":{"units":"minute","value":10},"formula":"","level":3,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":"niter, sulfur, and pine tar formed into a bead"},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"self","value":null},"save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":2,"mode":"level"},"school":"evo","source":"Elemental Evil Player's Companion pg 161","target":{"type":"creature","units":null,"value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.kPgSXym7mny4MDXz"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2393,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":138194,"sources":[{"pageNumber":161,"sourceId":4,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Damage"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/fire/explosion-embers-orange.webp","name":"Melf's Minute Meteors","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"nRVsc3eQb7itlwIr","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"save","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You attempt to beguile a humanoid that you can see within range. It must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be charmed by you for the duration. If you or creatures that are friendly to you are fighting it, it has advantage on the saving throw.</p>\n<p>While the target is charmed, you have a telepathic link with it as long as the two of you are on the same plane of existence. You can use this telepathic link to issue commands to the creature while you are conscious (no action required), which it does its best to obey. You can specify a simple and general course of action, such as \"Attack that creature,\" \"Run over there,\" or \"Fetch that object.\" If the creature completes the order and doesn't receive further direction from you, it defends and preserves itself to the best of its ability.</p>\n<p>You can use your action to take total and precise control of the target. Until the end of your next turn, the creature takes only the actions you choose, and doesn't do anything that you don't allow it to do. During this time you can also cause the creature to use a reaction, but this requires you to use your own reaction as well.</p>\n<p>Each time the target takes damage, it makes a new Wisdom saving throw against the spell. If the saving throw succeeds, the spell ends.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a 6th-level spell slot, the duration is concentration, up to 10 minutes. When you use a 7th-level spell slot, the duration is concentration, up to 1 hour. When you use a spell slot of 8th level or higher, the duration is concentration, up to 8 hours.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You attempt to beguile a humanoid that you can see within range. It must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be charmed by you for the duration. If you or creatures that are friendly to you are fighting it, it has advantage on the saving throw.</p>\n<p>While the target is charmed, you have a telepathic link with it as long as the two of you are on the same plane of existence. You can use this telepathic link to issue commands to the creature while you are conscious (no action required), which it does its best to obey. You can specify a simple and general course of action, such as \"Attack that creature,\" \"Run over there,\" or \"Fetch that object.\" If the creature completes the order and doesn't receive further direction from you, it defends and preserves itself to the best of its ability.</p>\n<p>You can use your action to take total and precise control of the target. Until the end of your next turn, the creature takes only the actions you choose, and doesn't do anything that you don't allow it to do. During this time you can also cause the creature to use a reaction, but this requires you to use your own reaction as well.</p>\n<p>Each time the target takes damage, it makes a new Wisdom saving throw against the spell. If the saving throw succeeds, the spell ends.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a 6th-level spell slot, the duration is concentration, up to 10 minutes. When you use a 7th-level spell slot, the duration is concentration, up to 1 hour. When you use a spell slot of 8th level or higher, the duration is concentration, up to 8 hours.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"minute","value":1},"formula":"","level":5,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":60},"save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"enc","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 235","target":{"type":"creature","units":null,"value":1,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.j9Lnf2offmEBBfsE"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2078,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":136663,"sources":[{"pageNumber":null,"sourceId":1,"sourceType":2},{"pageNumber":235,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Control"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/air/air-burst-spiral-large-pink.webp","name":"Dominate Person","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"nSJg9ocdli1gyrHn","data":{"ability":"","actionType":"other","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":"","type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>This spell is a minor magical trick that novice spellcasters use for practice. You create one of the following magical effects within range:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You create an instantaneous, harmless sensory effect, such as a shower of sparks, a puff of wind, faint musical notes, or an odd odor.</li>\n<li>You instantaneously light or snuff out a candle, a torch, or a small campfire.</li>\n<li>You instantaneously clean or soil an object no larger than 1 cubic foot.</li>\n<li>You chill, warm, or flavor up to 1 cubic foot of nonliving material for 1 hour.</li>\n<li>You make a color, a small mark, or a symbol appear on an object or a surface for 1 hour.</li>\n<li>You create a nonmagical trinket or an illusory image that can fit in your hand and that lasts until the end of your next turn.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br />If you cast this spell multiple times, you can have up to three of its non-instantaneous effects active at a time, and you can dismiss such an effect as an action.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>This spell is a minor magical trick that novice spellcasters use for practice. You create one of the following magical effects within range:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You create an instantaneous, harmless sensory effect, such as a shower of sparks, a puff of wind, faint musical notes, or an odd odor.</li>\n<li>You instantaneously light or snuff out a candle, a torch, or a small campfire.</li>\n<li>You instantaneously clean or soil an object no larger than 1 cubic foot.</li>\n<li>You chill, warm, or flavor up to 1 cubic foot of nonliving material for 1 hour.</li>\n<li>You make a color, a small mark, or a symbol appear on an object or a surface for 1 hour.</li>\n<li>You create a nonmagical trinket or an illusory image that can fit in your hand and that lasts until the end of your next turn.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br />If you cast this spell multiple times, you can have up to three of its non-instantaneous effects active at a time, and you can dismiss such an effect as an action.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"hour","value":1},"formula":"","level":0,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":10},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"trs","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 267","target":{"type":"","units":"","value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":"","per":"","value":null}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickDesc":{"value":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true},"quickOther":{"context":"","value":true},"quickProperties":{"value":true},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true,"value":false}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.2hb7du3X101CS89p"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2213,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":138586,"sources":[{"pageNumber":null,"sourceId":1,"sourceType":2},{"pageNumber":267,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Utility"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/fire/explosion-fireball-small-purple-orange.webp","name":"Prestidigitation","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"nTkXYER0BtVwLuhD","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"other","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"minute"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":true,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"a tiny piece of matter of the same type of the item you plan to create","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You pull wisps of shadow material from the Shadowfell to create a nonliving object of vegetable matter within range: soft goods, rope, wood, or something similar. You can also use this spell to create mineral objects such as stone, crystal, or metal. The object created must be no larger than a 5-foot cube, and the object must be of a form and material that you have seen before.</p>\n<p>The duration depends on the object's material. If the object is composed of multiple materials, use the shortest duration.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Material</th>\n<th>Duration</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Vegetable matter</td>\n<td>1 day</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Stone or crystal</td>\n<td>12 hours</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Precious metals</td>\n<td>1 hour</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Gems</td>\n<td>10 minutes</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Adamantine or mithral</td>\n<td>1 minute</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Using any material created by this spell as another spell's material component causes that spell to fail.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 6th level or higher, the cube increases by 5 feet for each slot level above 5th.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You pull wisps of shadow material from the Shadowfell to create a nonliving object of vegetable matter within range: soft goods, rope, wood, or something similar. You can also use this spell to create mineral objects such as stone, crystal, or metal. The object created must be no larger than a 5-foot cube, and the object must be of a form and material that you have seen before.</p>\n<p>The duration depends on the object's material. If the object is composed of multiple materials, use the shortest duration.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Material</th>\n<th>Duration</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Vegetable matter</td>\n<td>1 day</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Stone or crystal</td>\n<td>12 hours</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Precious metals</td>\n<td>1 hour</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Gems</td>\n<td>10 minutes</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Adamantine or mithral</td>\n<td>1 minute</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Using any material created by this spell as another spell's material component causes that spell to fail.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 6th level or higher, the cube increases by 5 feet for each slot level above 5th.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"spec","value":""},"formula":"","level":5,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":"a tiny piece of matter of the same type of the item you plan to create"},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":30},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"ill","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 229","target":{"type":"cube","units":"ft","value":5,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.RCIE2n8pSpRVRrQw"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2055,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":136472,"sources":[{"pageNumber":