{"_id":"nVVt8Uwsvq9xmofx","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"rsak","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You create three rays of fire and hurl them at targets within range. You can hurl them at one target or several.</p>\n<p>Make a ranged spell attack for each ray. On a hit, the target takes 2d6 fire damage.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, you create one additional ray for each slot level above 2nd.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You create three rays of fire and hurl them at targets within range. You can hurl them at one target or several.</p>\n<p>Make a ranged spell attack for each ray. On a hit, the target takes 2d6 fire damage.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, you create one additional ray for each slot level above 2nd.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"inst","value":""},"formula":"","level":2,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":120},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"evo","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 273","target":{"type":"creature","units":null,"value":1,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.D3viBb8RDN15PBPk"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2238,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"