{"_id":"qJzjYb5cxslXb3n8","data":{"ability":"","actionType":"other","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":"","type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>You make yourself--including your clothing, armor, weapons, and other belongings on your person--look different until the spell ends or until you use your action to dismiss it. You can seem 1 foot shorter or taller and can appear thin, fat, or in between. You can't change your body type, so you must adopt a form that has the same basic arrangement of limbs. Otherwise, the extent of the illusion is up to you.</p>\n<p>The changes wrought by this spell fail to hold up to physical inspection. For example, if you use this spell to add a hat to your outfit, objects pass through the hat, and anyone who touches it would feel nothing or would feel your head and hair. If you use this spell to appear thinner than you are, the hand of someone who reaches out to touch you would bump into you while it was seemingly still in midair.</p>\n<p>To discern that you are disguised, a creature can use its action to inspect your appearance and must succeed on an Intelligence (Investigation) check against your spell save DC.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>You make yourself--including your clothing, armor, weapons, and other belongings on your person--look different until the spell ends or until you use your action to dismiss it. You can seem 1 foot shorter or taller and can appear thin, fat, or in between. You can't change your body type, so you must adopt a form that has the same basic arrangement of limbs. Otherwise, the extent of the illusion is up to you.</p>\n<p>The changes wrought by this spell fail to hold up to physical inspection. For example, if you use this spell to add a hat to your outfit, objects pass through the hat, and anyone who touches it would feel nothing or would feel your head and hair. If you use this spell to appear thinner than you are, the hand of someone who reaches out to touch you would bump into you while it was seemingly still in midair.</p>\n<p>To discern that you are disguised, a creature can use its action to inspect your appearance and must succeed on an Intelligence (Investigation) check against your spell save DC.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"hour","value":1},"formula":"","level":1,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"self","value":null},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"ill","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 233","target":{"type":"self","units":"","value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":"0","per":"","value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickDesc":{"altValue":true,"value":true},"quickFlavor":{"altValue":true,"value":true},"quickOther":{"altValue":true,"context":"","value":true},"quickProperties":{"altValue":true,"value":true},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true,"value":false}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.EmDwOenKgI1Gv6mz"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2069,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":136608,"sources":[{"pageNumber":null,"sourceId":1,"sourceType":2},{"pageNumber":233,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Shapechanging"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-hold-teal-blue.webp","name":"Disguise Self","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"qOvvAkK61NnyGCkO","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"save","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"action"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["4d10","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>Drawing on the deepest fears of a group of creatures, you create illusory creatures in their minds, visible only to them. Each creature in a 30-foot-radius sphere centered on a point of your choice within range must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, a creature becomes frightened for the duration. The illusion calls on the creature's deepest fears, manifesting its worst nightmares as an implacable threat. At the end of each of the frightened creature's turns, it must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or take 4d10 psychic damage. On a successful save, the spell ends for that creature.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>Drawing on the deepest fears of a group of creatures, you create illusory creatures in their minds, visible only to them. Each creature in a 30-foot-radius sphere centered on a point of your choice within range must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, a creature becomes frightened for the duration. The illusion calls on the creature's deepest fears, manifesting its worst nightmares as an implacable threat. At the end of each of the frightened creature's turns, it must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or take 4d10 psychic damage. On a successful save, the spell ends for that creature.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"minute","value":1},"formula":"","level":9,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"ft","value":120},"save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"ill","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 288","target":{"type":"sphere","units":"ft","value":30,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.bbW0BUIB0eHFEkjj"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2300,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":138946,"sources":[{"pageNumber":null,"sourceId":1,"sourceType":2},{"pageNumber":288,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Damage","Control"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-monster-grin-green.webp","name":"Weird","permission":{"3AYHMWdZOlxF9nZC":3,"default":0},"sort":0,"type":"spell"}
{"_id":"qUlIH6PyAnrzsJY9","data":{"ability":null,"actionType":"other","activation":{"condition":"","cost":1,"type":"reaction"},"attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","components":{"concentration":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"somatic":true,"value":"","vocal":true},"consume":{"amount":null,"target":null,"type":""},"critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"description":{"chat":"<p>An invisible barrier of magical force appears and protects you. Until the start of your next turn, you have a +5 bonus to AC, including against the triggering attack, and you take no damage from <strong>magic missile</strong>.</p>","unidentified":"","value":"<p>An invisible barrier of magical force appears and protects you. Until the start of your next turn, you have a +5 bonus to AC, including against the triggering attack, and you take no damage from <strong>magic missile</strong>.</p>"},"duration":{"units":"round","value":1},"formula":"","level":1,"materials":{"consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0,"value":""},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"range":{"long":null,"units":"self","value":null},"save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"scaling":{"formula":"","mode":"none"},"school":"abj","source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook pg 275","target":{"type":"self","units":null,"value":null,"width":null},"uses":{"max":0,"per":null,"value":0}},"effects":[],"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"quickCharges":{"altValue":{"resource":true,"use":true},"value":{"resource":true,"use":true}},"quickVersatile":{"altValue":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.ddb-import-haven-spells.4Iuy8lIwFUJGvPfS"},"ddbimporter":{"definitionId":2247,"dndbeyond":{"castAtLevel":null,"level":null,"lookup":"generic","lookupName":"generic"},"entityTypeId":435869154,"id":138701,"sources":[{"pageNumber":null,"sourceId":1,"sourceType":2},{"pageNumber":275,"sourceId":2,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Warding"]}},"folder":null,"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-glowing-triangle-magenta.webp","n